IM["Interaction Manager\nUpstream semantic signal source"]:::process
BIC["Blueprint Interface Contract\nArtist-facing named parameters · typed + bounded"]:::control
MMC["Mosaic Master Controller\nOrchestration root · global state owner"]:::runtime
GSB["Global State Blend\nCross-zone blend weights · presence envelope"]:::runtime
ETC["Effect Timelines · Curves\nAnimated response · curve-driven gains"]:::runtime
ZLB["Zone Logic Blueprints\nPer-zone effect dispatch · spatial logic"]:::runtime

subgraph ZONE_OUT [" Zone Logic Outputs "]
    RF(["Reveal Field\nAlpha mask · presence-driven opacity"]):::output
    GE(["Glow · Emissive Lift\nEmissive gain · zone-local intensity"]):::output
    DR(["Distortion · Ripple · Lift\nDistort vector · ripple coefficient"]):::output
end

GID>"Blueprint = orchestration + tuning surface · not a raw tracking parser"]:::guide

IM -->|semantic signals| BIC
BIC -->|contracted params| MMC
MMC --> GSB
MMC --> ETC
MMC --> ZLB
ZLB -->|alpha mask| RF
ZLB -->|emissive gain| GE
ZLB -->|distort vector| DR

